RawLine: SDM_1101604613,可惜你沒答對問題，我只能給你熬過藥湯的當歸。但只要多煮一會兒，香氣也不會輸給新鮮的當歸才是。,可惜你没答对问题，我只能给你熬过药汤的当归。但只要多煮一会儿，香气也不会输给新鲜的当归才是。

Items.mt: It's a pity that you didn't answer the question correctly, so I can only give you danggui that has been boiled in a medicinal soup. But if you cook it for a little longer, the aroma will not be inferior to that of fresh angelica.
